{"sections":{"dynamic_slideshow_WMJGGb":{"type":"dynamic-slideshow","blocks":{"slide_AqAtrP":{"type":"slide","settings":{"background_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Desktop_Slideshow-5.png","mobile_background_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/20.png","title":"MP's Guide to: Finding the Perfect Fit","text":"A Complete Jewellery Size Guide for Every Piercing","color":"#ffffff","link":"","text_alignment":"left","button_one_label":"","button_one_link":"","button_one_style":"primary","button_two_label":"","button_two_link":"","button_two_style":"primary","show_overlay":false,"overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":50}}},"block_order":["slide_AqAtrP"],"settings":{"enable_autoplay":true,"autoplay_duration":8,"slideshow_width":"full","slideshow_height":"small","slideshow_height_mobile":"medium","slideshow_text_below_image":true}},"main":{"type":"page","disabled":true,"settings":{}},"dynamic_rich_text_WyhVhR":{"type":"dynamic-rich-text","settings":{"width":"wide","title":"Where can I wear my jewellery?","text":"<p>Most body jewellery can be used in more than one piercing area. That's the great thing about jewellery, the possibilities and styles are endless! We've put together this size guide that can help you choose the perfect-fit items from our store, however, for the most comfortable fit, safety and style, please ensure you know your exact piercing sizes. If unknown, it is best to consult with a local piercer.<\/p><h4>What jewellery is recommended for fresh piercings?<\/h4><p>When getting a new piercing, choosing the right size is crucial for proper healing. Initially, looser fit jewellery is recommended to allow airflow and reduced pressure on the pierced area. Proper cleaning is also required for new piercings to reduce any risk of infection.<\/p><h4>The Perfect Fit<\/h4><p>Once your piercing has fully healed, opt for jewellery that is a better fit and of quality materials to avoid risk of reaction. A tighter fit jewellery piece can also be worn for a more polished 